sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PU as Platform User
participant FE as Browser UI
participant APP as Express App
participant TM as Tenant Middleware
participant VM as Validation Middleware
participant AC as Auth Controller
participant CC as Compliance Controller
participant OS as OAuth Service
participant DB as Database
participant ENC as Encryption
participant TS as Tenant Session
participant STR as Tool Strategy
participant RES as Tool Resolver
participant MCP as MCP Client
participant REST as REST Client
participant RN as Response Normalizer
participant EE as Evaluation Engine
participant RF as Report Formatter
participant OP as OAuth Provider
participant EMCP as External MCP Server
participant API as Provider REST API

rect rgb(230, 242, 255)
Note over PU,FE: Client Actions
PU->>FE: Open app
FE->>APP: GET /api/auth/{provider}/status
end

rect rgb(232, 255, 238)
Note over APP,RF: Our System (App, DB, Services)
APP->>TM: Validate tenant session cookie
TM->>TS: Verify token
alt valid session
  TS-->>TM: tenantId
  TM-->>APP: next
  APP->>VM: Validate request
  APP->>AC: status
  AC->>OS: status(provider, tenantId)
  OS->>DB: getToken
  DB-->>OS: token or null
  OS-->>AC: connected flag
  AC-->>FE: status response
else invalid session
  TM-->>FE: 401
end
end

rect rgb(230, 242, 255)
PU->>FE: Click connect
FE->>APP: GET /api/auth/{provider}/connect
end

rect rgb(232, 255, 238)
APP->>TM: tenant middleware
TM-->>APP: allow
APP->>VM: Validate provider
APP->>AC: connect
AC->>OS: getConnectUrl
OS->>DB: saveOAuthState
OS-->>AC: authorize URL
AC-->>FE: redirect
end

rect rgb(255, 239, 230)
Note over OP,API: External Servers (GitHub/GitLab/Bitbucket)
FE->>OP: authorize
OP-->>FE: callback with code and state
end

rect rgb(232, 255, 238)
FE->>APP: GET callback
APP->>TM: callback bypass
APP->>VM: Validate params
APP->>AC: callback
AC->>OS: handleCallback
OS->>DB: getOAuthState
alt invalid state
  OS-->>AC: error
  AC-->>FE: error response
else valid state
  OS->>DB: deleteOAuthState
  OS->>OP: exchange code for token
  OP-->>OS: access token
  OS->>ENC: encrypt token
  OS->>DB: upsertToken
  AC->>TS: create session token
  TS-->>AC: signed cookie
  AC-->>FE: set cookie and redirect dashboard
end

FE->>APP: GET repos list
APP->>TM: verify session
APP->>VM: Validate query
APP->>AC: repos
AC->>OS: listRepos
OS->>DB: getToken
OS->>ENC: decrypt token
OS->>API: fetch repos
API-->>OS: repos payload
OS-->>AC: normalized repos
AC-->>FE: repos response
end

rect rgb(230, 242, 255)
PU->>FE: Run compliance check
FE->>APP: POST /api/compliance/evaluate-standard
end

rect rgb(232, 255, 238)
APP->>TM: verify session
APP->>VM: Validate body
APP->>CC: evaluateStandard
CC->>CC: Filter ISO27001 controls to 8.8, 8.9
CC->>OS: getAccessToken
OS->>DB: getToken
OS->>ENC: decrypt token
OS-->>CC: access token

loop each selected repo
  loop control 8.8, 8.9
  CC->>STR: executeTool
  STR->>MCP: listTools
  alt MCP available
    MCP->>EMCP: tools/list or tools/call
    EMCP-->>MCP: evidence
    MCP-->>STR: MCP evidence
  else fallback
    STR->>REST: callTool
    REST->>API: REST call
    API-->>REST: REST evidence
    REST-->>STR: fallback evidence
  end
  STR->>RES: resolve mode
  STR->>RN: normalize evidence
  RN-->>STR: standardized payload
  STR-->>CC: evidence
  CC->>EE: evaluate control
  EE-->>CC: verdict
  CC->>RF: format report row
  RF-->>CC: row
  end
end

CC-->>FE: final report response
FE-->>PU: render results

opt disconnect
  FE->>APP: POST /api/auth/{provider}/disconnect
  APP->>AC: disconnect
  AC->>OS: revoke and delete token
  OS->>DB: deleteToken
  AC-->>FE: disconnected
end
end
